dc_title_s: EMS Response Districts St. Croix County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: [Emergency Service Zones identifying fire protection, emergency medical service and law enforcement agency response areas.]This data layer represents Emergency Medical Service (EMS) response districts in St. Croix County, Wisconsin in 2020.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data for this county, please visit: https://gis-scccdd.opendata.arcgis.com/
